    <briefdescription>
<para>represents both translational and rotational acceleration. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class represents an acceleration twist. A acceleration twist is the combination of translational acceleration and rotational acceleration applied at one point. represents the combination of a force and a torque.</para><para>This class represents a <ref refid="classKDL_1_1Wrench" kindref="compound">Wrench</ref>. A <ref refid="classKDL_1_1Wrench" kindref="compound">Wrench</ref> is the force and torque applied at a point </para>    </detaileddescription>
